Read the documentation in qemu-doc.html or on http://wiki.qemu.org

- QEMU team

- Need the SDL library
sudo apt-get install libsdl1.2-dev

- Need Ninja since 5.2.0
sudo apt-get install ninja-build

Configure options for arm:

./configure --target-list=arm-softmmu --disable-attr --disable-werror --disable-docs

Configure options for risc-v:

./configure --target-list=riscv64-softmmu --disable-attr --disable-werror --disable-docs
